    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A new subspecies of Seseli gummiferum (Apiaceae) from Ilgaz Mountain National Park, northern Turkey" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure5>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure6> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Seseli gummiferum subsp. ilgazense A. Duran, Oe. Cetin & M. Oeztuerk, subsp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59479" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Cross section of fruit: emb = embriyo; dvb = dorsal vascular bundle; ex = exocarp; cdv = central dorsal vittae; es = endosperm; lvb = lateral vascular bundle; ldv = lateral dorsal vittae; ae = aerenchyma; cv = commissural vittae; cvb = carpophore vascular bundle; covb = commissural vascular bundle. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59480" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Seseli gummiferum subsp. ilgazense. A trifid and entire bracteoles B lateral umbel C general aspects D habitat and general view of type locality. Photo by A. Duran." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59481" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Comparison of Seseli gummiferum fruits. Seseli corymbosum fruits. A general view B surface details. Seseli corymbosum: C general view D surface details. Seseli gummiferum subsp. ilgazense: E general view F surface details." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59482" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Distribution of Seseli gummiferum subsp. ilgazense (♦), Seseli gummiferum subsp. gummiferum (●) and Seseli corymbosum (■) in Turkey." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59483" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.56.5755.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. The neighbour joining tree generated using nrITS DNA sequences of some Seseli taxa and Pimpinella saxifraga." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/59484" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

